thread.title: Micheal

author: Micheal
title: Micheal
text:
The staff were very helpful in helping me build my project. They discussed options and gave confident and professional opinions when asked for advice.
I went in to pick up my order and had a great chat with the staff, and it was clear they really get excited with quality products.
The prices are good, and the quality is great. (no more vista print!)
Looking forward to many more projects.
